How to Use the Web App

Access the Platform: Click the live deployment link provided below.

Enter Customer Details: On the left sidebar, input the customer financial information including Annual Income, Credit Score, Loan Term, Purpose, Debt-to-Income Ratio, Employment Status, and Grade.

Generate Predictions: Click the Assess Risk and Predict Loan button.

View Results: The AI will display the Risk Category, Predicted Loan Amount, and Deep Learning Score.

How to Run the Code Locally

Clone the Repository using: git clone https://github.com/rangaganbir/ANTL202-Final-Project-Deployment

Install Dependencies using: pip install -r requirements.txt

Run the Application using: streamlit run app.py

Project Files app.py: The main application script. pkl and h5 files: The trained AI models. loan_dataset_20000.csv: The historical data used for training. Project_Complete_Code.ipynb: The source code for model development.

Deployment Live App: https://ut8rrnujtrrnpau6bwmb6e.streamlit.app

